# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ATTRIBUTE ANNOTATIONS FROM EXISTING RP QUESTIONS
#
# These attributes already have scalar questions in TypeDB.
# We add the annotation relation so TypeDB queries can join
# to the question text directly.
#
# NOT duplicating the 31 annotations from seed_attribute_annotations.tql.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── tax_distribution_basket ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

